The paper discusses collaborative tagging and faceted search on structured P2P systems, which involves topics related to distributed systems (cs.DS) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed approach also involves graph maintenance, which is a topic in social networks (cs.SI) and databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper discusses scalability issues, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY).
